{"tid":915559,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"科學家倡在大氣層撒化學物　調暗陽光對抗全球暖化","createTime":"2018-11-25T05:34:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T07:35:08.000Z","uid":212399,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"0bd04f06b7518c3a526edcff05ab3bbd2e487f31","tid":915559,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T05:34:24.000Z","msg":"小學時每當有人惡言相向對你謾罵，我們都喊出「閘住反彈無回頭」作還擊，想不到這招竟可能是救地球的方法？<br />\n哈佛大學及耶魯大學的科學家近日在《環境研究快報》（Environmental Research Letters）發表研究報告，提出可以在地球大氣層噴灑大量化學物，調暗從太陽射進地球的陽光光度，並反射部分陽光，希望藉此把全球暖化速度減半。不過，這項技術仍是紙上談兵，「十劃未有一撇」，亦有可能會危害農作物產量，導致乾旱或極端天氣。<br />\n<br />\n科學家提出「平流層氣溶膠注入」技術（SAI，Stratospheric aerosol injection），利用專門設計的高空飛機、氣球或大型海軍炮，在19公里高空向地球平流層下層噴灑大量硫酸鹽顆粒，藉此反射陽光。<br />\n這項技術仍停留在構想階段，科學家亦尚未研發適合的飛機。不過研究人員稱，在技術層面上「其實唔難」，預料耗資約35億美元（約273億港元）可在15年內（2033年）實現技術；每年營運成本則約22.5億美元（約175億港元）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2132894/org/261228162df22df45456d4cb4fb12a98.jpg/GBV92wyYZLCHNFEZ2T8wh4qdSE8tgsekJIFjgySBY4M?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2132894%2Forg%2F261228162df22df45456d4cb4fb12a98.jpg%2FGBV92wyYZLCHNFEZ2T8wh4qdSE8tgsekJIFjgySBY4M%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=aab575ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n平流層氣溶膠注入：科學家提出SAI，利用專門設計的高空飛機、氣球或大型海軍炮，在平流層噴灑大量硫酸鹽顆粒，藉此反射陽光。<br />\n由於SAI未經驗證，研究人員承認項目有潛在風險，可能會危害農作物產量，導致乾旱或極端天氣，亦需要南北半球多個國家之間協調。<br />\n溫室氣體排放是導致全球暖化的主因，由於SAI無法解決溫室氣體排放問題，不少科學家對此均持懷疑態度，他們認為控制太陽亮度較控制溫室氣體排放更糟糕，而且長遠而言，SAI的成本更高，風險更大。<br />\n芝加哥大學地球物理科學系教授阿徹（David Archer）認為，SAI只是一個暫時封住問題的「急救膠布」，若人們不減少排放溫室氣體，最終仍是會面臨全球暖化。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2132895/org/647bb769923197db4189d6345855a2a0.jpg/mE-V9ApC_pqAMnnFbAgMspJRYnlXQ9xjrdlNlq3ZTZY?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2132895%2Forg%2F647bb769923197db4189d6345855a2a0.jpg%2FmE-V9ApC_pqAMnnFbAgMspJRYnlXQ9xjrdlNlq3ZTZY%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=6a6754b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n平流層氣溶膠注入：不少科學家對SAI持懷疑態度，指控制太陽亮度較控制溫室氣體排放更糟糕，而且長遠而言，SAI的成本更高，風險更大。"},{"pid":"2af9124c19e4a16be02beb4aafe9859a968acd80","tid":915559,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T05:35:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"161f8eec53c3e932a274c6b357bfffcd30c3726d","tid":915559,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T05:35:47.000Z","msg":"Link?"},{"pid":"c81a35d8423f523521710a6309450f43b8a6cdca","tid":915559,"uid":52358,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T05:36:26.000Z","msg":"matrix the second renaissance<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b62590d8341941786fa6dd19b60fd9b8d49de9b","tid":915559,"uid":42188,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T05:37:18.000Z","msg":"支那已經做緊"},{"pid":"57e643441662ffd63c83cc09b28f67b9b729c6fc","tid":915559,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c81a35d8423f523521710a6309450f43b8a6cdca","tid":915559,"uid":52358,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T05:36:26.000Z","msg":"matrix the second renaissance<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T05:38:07.000Z","msg":"我都記起matrix <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b47dd93a8405a031711534d066fec3bbea09aee3","tid":915559,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"161f8eec53c3e932a274c6b357bfffcd30c3726d","tid":915559,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T05:35:47.000Z","msg":"Link?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T05:38:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1088/1748-9326/aae98d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fiopscience.iop.org%2Farticle%2F10.1088%2F1748-9326%2Faae98d&d=tKJvl9cJ4JGxj2E%2F8UpRZDACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=25820b15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">htt